{"name": "gatoroboto_b_side", "game": "Gato Roboto B-Side", "version": "0.6.1", "hidden": false, "groups": [{"name": "Game Options", "options": [{"name": "progression_balancing", "display_name": "Progression Balancing", "description": "A system that can move progression earlier, to try and prevent the player from getting stuck and bored early.\n\nA lower setting means more getting stuck. A higher setting means less getting stuck.", "randomizable": true, "visibility": 15, "type": "NamedRange", "default": 50, "min": 0, "max": 99, "presets": {"disabled": 0, "normal": 50, "extreme": 99}}, {"name": "accessibility", "display_name": "Accessibility", "description": "Set rules for reachability of your items/locations.\n\n**Full:** ensure everything can be reached and acquired.\n\n**Minimal:** ensure what is needed to reach your goal can be acquired.", "randomizable": true, "visibility": 15, "type": "Choice", "default": 0, "choices": [{"name": "full", "display_name": "Full", "value": 0}, {"name": "minimal", "display_name": "Minimal", "value": 2}]}], "collapsed": false}, {"name": "Logic Options", "options": [{"name": "use_smallmech", "display_name": "Use Smallmech", "description": "Includes logic for the Smallmech glitch.\nIn \"Vanilla\" difficulty, this will force the Lava Cooled event to be at Cooler.", "randomizable": true, "visibility": 15, "type": "Toggle", "default": false}, {"name": "use_watermech", "display_name": "Use Watermech", "description": "Includes logic for the Watermech glitch.", "randomizable": true, "visibility": 15, "type": "Toggle", "default": false}, {"name": "gato_tech", "display_name": "Gato Tech", "description": "Difficulty of strategies.\n\n\"Medium\" is recommended for normal players. You might have to do some tricks done in the Any% speedrun if you enable glitches.\n\n\"Hard\" includes a bunch of difficult or obscure strategies, which require advanced knowledge.\n\n\"Vanilla\" is a special difficulty, with a raised difficulty for the very best. It will:\n- remove the crash fixes in heater core\n- include the logic for the standard cat vent skip and vent mashing\n- assume that you can avoid a hardlock in ventilation by either routing properly or resetting the savefile (not currently!)", "randomizable": true, "visibility": 15, "type": "Choice", "default": 1, "choices": [{"name": "medium", "display_name": "Medium", "value": 1}, {"name": "hard", "display_name": "Hard", "value": 2}, {"name": "vanilla_expert", "display_name": "Vanilla Expert", "value": 3}]}, {"name": "nexus_start", "display_name": "Nexus Start", "description": "Start in the Nexus instead of the Landing Site.\nAllows for some logic checks without rocket", "randomizable": true, "visibility": 15, "type": "Toggle", "default": false}], "collapsed": false}, {"name": "Goal Options", "options": [{"name": "aqueduct_goal", "display_name": "Aqueduct Goal", "description": "Required amount of \"Water Level\" required to enter Incubator.", "randomizable": true, "visibility": 15, "type": "Range", "default": 3, "min": 0, "max": 3}, {"name": "heatercore_goal", "display_name": "Heater Core Goal", "description": "Required amount of \"Lava Cooled\" required to enter Incubator.", "randomizable": true, "visibility": 15, "type": "Range", "default": 1, "min": 0, "max": 1}, {"name": "ventilation_goal", "display_name": "Ventilation Goal", "description": "Required amount of \"Vent Level\" required to enter Incubator.", "randomizable": true, "visibility": 15, "type": "Range", "default": 3, "min": 0, "max": 3}], "collapsed": false}, {"name": "Checksanity", "options": [{"name": "loresanity", "display_name": "Loresanity", "description": "Add lore buttons/terminals to the itempool.\nIncludes the main terminal in nexus and the two secret lore spot in nexus.", "randomizable": true, "visibility": 15, "type": "Toggle", "default": false}], "collapsed": false}, {"name": "Technical Stuff", "options": [{"name": "local_start", "display_name": "Force Local Start", "description": "Makes the 